data.title: Teamsters Local 986 Santa Maria
data.text:
Teamsters have been serving Union families on the Central Coast for over 70 years. We have a proud history of Union activism and leadership that spans 4 generations. Craft and service areas that we represent include the following:

Sanitation Drivers/Employees • Bakery/Cake Drivers • Professional Employees • Government Contractors • Freight Drivers • Dairy Drivers • Public Sector Employees • Liquor Drivers • Transit Drivers • Clerical Employees • Utility Employees • Provision Drivers • Linen Drivers • Soft Drink Drivers • Construction Labor • Rock, Sand and Gravel • Lumber Workers • Aerospace Workers
